UPDATE users_compliance
            SET
              requested = $2,
              signed = $3,
              e_delivery_consented = $4,
              tin_matched = $5,
              last_checked = $6,
              external_request_id = $7,
              reference_id = $8,
              form_type = $9,
              requires_manual_review = $10
            WHERE id = $1
